          "utf8": "and she co-founded\nthe Young Pride Club in Chiang Mai."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 418700,
      "dDurationMs": 4740,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "For me, I'm thinking from the\nperspective of young Thai queer person."
