      "tStartMs": 561000,
      "dDurationMs": 4560,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "inclusive society does allows an open\nfor LGBTQ people."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 565560,
      "dDurationMs": 3840,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And in Thailand, religions play\nan important role to society."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 569400,
      "dDurationMs": 2880,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "You can't just like,\nseparate them from each other."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 572280,
      "dDurationMs": 6480,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "And in Buddhism, there's no principles\nthat against LGBTQ so you can be LGBTQ"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 578760,
      "dDurationMs": 3900,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "is not a sin or it's not nothing.\nYou can just do your things."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 582660,
      "dDurationMs": 3900,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Only one thing is that you can't get\ninto monastic being transgenders"
