      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 596920,
      "dDurationMs": 6080,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "us to be more open compared to other\nreligions that might see it as a sin."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 603000,
      "dDurationMs": 5200,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "Does that mean that in Thailand, people\ncan identify as their preferred gender"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 608200,
      "dDurationMs": 3540,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "and that's recognised legally,\nor is that still an issue?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 611740,
      "dDurationMs": 2300,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So that is a separate law and Thai"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 614040,
      "dDurationMs": 3360,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "people can't just identify themselves\nat their wish"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 617400,
      "dDurationMs": 2800,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "or according\nto their gender preference."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 620200,
      "dDurationMs": 2900,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So it has actually been proposed\nthis year as well."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 623100,
      "dDurationMs": 4660,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "This law, this bill but it's got\nrejected back in February this year."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "tStartMs": 627760,
      "dDurationMs": 3440,
      "segs": [
        {
          "utf8": "So in 2019, Taiwan's parliament\nbecame the first in Asia"
        }
